      <link>https://mastodon.jakewharton.com/@jw/115657573698966150</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Dec 2025 20:42:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I don't use the Compose BOM, and I don't think you should either. The advantages it claims to provide are less than it actually does. Let's defuse the Compose BOM.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://jakewharton.com/defuse-the-compose-bom/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;jakewharton.com/defuse-the-com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;pose-bom/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
